{"article_id":"khBbKnwqfQs4paLw","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON-President Trump said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"he doesn ' t believe","depth":10},{"id":2,"text":"congressional negotiators will strike a deal over border-wall funding","depth":11},{"id":3,"text":"that he could accept","depth":11},{"id":4,"text":"and vowed","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"that he would build a wall anyway ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"using emergency powers","depth":12},{"id":7,"text":"if need be .","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"Mr. Trump , in an interview , assessed the chances","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"of whether a newly formed group of 17 lawmakers could craft a deal before the next government-funding lapse , in less than three weeks :","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"\" I personally think","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"it ' s less than 50-50 ,","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"but you have a lot of very good people on that board . \"","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"He made his comments","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"as hundreds of thousands of federal employees prepared to head back to work Monday","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"following the president ' s move Friday","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"to reopen the government after the 35-day partial shutdown ,","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"even without funding for his long-promised wall along the border with Mexico .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"The group of 17 lawmakers is now tasked with hashing out a longer-term deal on border security and , potentially , broader immigration issues .","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Both topics are politically charged and difficult to navigate ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"just as they were in late December ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"when Mr. Trump first refused to sign any spending bills","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"that didn ' t include at least $ 5.7 billion","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"to go toward building a border wall .","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"Asked if he would accept less than $ 5.7 billion in the next round of negotiations ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mr. Trump said :","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"\" I doubt it , \"","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"adding ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"\" I have to do it right . \"","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Democrats are firmly opposed to the concept of a physical wall ,","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"but they have been willing to fund replacement fencing , levees and bollard barriers , in addition to more immigration judges , border agents and technology .","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"On Sunday , Democratic leaders reiterated","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"that they support border-security measures","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and would negotiate","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"now that the government is open .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"\" Shutdowns are not legitimate negotiating tactics","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"when there ' s a public-policy disagreement between two branches of government , \"","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"Rep. Hakeem Jeffries of New York , chairman of the House Democratic caucus , said on NBC .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"In the interview Sunday , Mr. Trump also made clear","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"he was skeptical about any deal","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"that trades wall money for a wider immigration overhaul .","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"\" I doubt it , \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"he said ,","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"when asked","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"if he would agree to citizenship for a group of immigrants","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"illegally brought to the U.S. as children ,","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"known as Dreamers ,","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"in exchange for border-wall funding .","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"\" That ' s a separate subject","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to be taken up at a separate time , \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"said Mr. Trump , a Republican .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"Earlier this month , the president offered three years of temporary protections for Dreamers as part of a broader proposal ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"but Democrats said","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"they wanted more permanent protections ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"including a path to citizenship ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"for those immigrants .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"In the interview , Mr. Trump said","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"he wouldn ' t rule out another shutdown ,","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"calling it \" certainly an option . \"","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"After a shutdown","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that has been bruising for federal workers","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"and that taxed the wider economy ,","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"the White House ' s acting chief of staff , Mick Mulvaney , said on CBS on Sunday","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"that workers by the end of the week should receive their first paychecks in more than a month .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"The White House budget office published over the weekend a checklist","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"for government agencies","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"to consider","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"as they reopen ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"recommending , among other things ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that they have adequate staffing","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"to process payroll and employee benefits .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"But Mr. Trump ' s comments make clear","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"that","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"if keeping the government open hinges on the issue of immigration ,","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"the path forward will be tricky .","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"Congress has struggled for years to tackle a broader overhaul of the immigration system ,","depth":6},{"id":76,"text":"and","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"while lawmakers were hopeful","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that Congress and the White House would be eager to avoid another shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"persuading Mr. Trump to sign it may remain a separate challenge .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"Adding to that challenge for Mr. Trump :","depth":6},{"id":81,"text":"His leverage on the immigration issue has only diminished","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"since he took office .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"Republicans ,","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"who controlled Congress for much of his presidency ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"lost the House majority in the November elections ,","depth":6},{"id":86,"text":"and polling shows","depth":6},{"id":87,"text":"voters largely blamed Mr. Trump for a shutdown","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"that left about 800,000 federal workers without pay .","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"Over the weekend , Mr. Trump took heat from some conservative commentators","depth":5},{"id":90,"text":"who said","depth":6},{"id":91,"text":"he had caved to Democrats","depth":7},{"id":92,"text":"for reopening the government","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"without wall funding .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"Commentator Ann Coulter , for example , described Mr. Trump as a \" wimp . \"","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"\" I hear","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"she ' s become very hostile , \"","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Mr. Trump said in the interview .","depth":7},{"id":98,"text":"\" Maybe I didn ' t return her phone call or something . \"","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"Now the focus shifts to the lawmakers","depth":4},{"id":100,"text":"tasked with coming to an agreement .","depth":4},{"id":101,"text":"Led by House Appropriations Committee Chairwoman Nita Lowey","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"( D. , N.Y. ) ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"the group is expected to hold its first public meeting this week .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"Its roster is drawn from members from both chambers ' appropriations committees ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"which draft the spending bills","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"that fund the government ,","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"and includes some lawmakers","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"deeply versed in immigration policy .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"Seven of the 17 total members are senators ,","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"including four Republicans and three Democrats .","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"There are 10 House lawmakers ,","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"including six Democrats and four Republicans .","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"Any final compromise would need bipartisan support","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"to advance to a vote before both chambers .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"None of the lawmakers are bomb-throwers","depth":6},{"id":116,"text":"likely to buck their party ' s leaders ,","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"who will retain control over the biggest decisions ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"including the final price tag and whether anything resembling a wall","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"will be funded .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"\" I ' m going to remain optimistic...","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"if you look at the impetus from both sides ,","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"the shutdown was a miserable experience for everybody , \"","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"Sen. Shelley Moore Capito","depth":8},{"id":124,"text":"( R. , W.Va. ) ,","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"a member of the group , said Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"\" There ' s a lot","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"that tells me","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"we may not get there ,","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"but there ' s more","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that ' s telling me","depth":8},{"id":131,"text":"we have the urge","depth":8},{"id":132,"text":"to demonstrate","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"we can reach a consensus","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"or we ' re signaling to the American people","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"there ' s going to be two years of this","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"[ fighting ]","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"all of the time . \"","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"The thorniest question is likely to be what kinds of physical barriers would be funded along the border .","depth":3},{"id":139,"text":"Mr. Trump has been insistent on a wall","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"in order to deliver on his signature campaign promise ,","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"while Democrats have been equally resistant to one .","depth":7},{"id":142,"text":"\" Have I not been clear on a wall ? \"","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"( D. , Calif. )","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"said Friday .","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"\" I ' ve been very clear on the wall . \"","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"Asked about the form of barrier","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"he would accept on the border with Mexico ,","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"Mr. Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"\" I have to see what it is .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"As long as it can stop criminals , gangs , human trafficking and drugs ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"I ' m open to anything .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"But the only thing","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"that will work","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"is a very strong form of physical barrier . \"","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"But Democrats and Republicans often use different rhetoric","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"when describing the same provisions ,","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"suggesting","depth":8},{"id":159,"text":"they may be able to agree on some kind of funding","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"that","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"Republicans would consider a wall","depth":11},{"id":162,"text":"but Democrats would say","depth":11},{"id":163,"text":"constitutes border security .","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"\" We ' ve talked past each other to a certain extent , particularly on the notion of barriers , \"","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"Sen . Rob Portman","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"( R. , Ohio )","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"told reporters Friday .","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"\" I don ' t think","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"we ' re that far apart . \"","depth":8},{"id":170,"text":"In the Senate , the appropriations committee in June 2018 approved a bill","depth":8},{"id":171,"text":"funding the Homeland Security Department ,","depth":9},{"id":172,"text":"which oversees the border ,","depth":9},{"id":173,"text":"that included $ 1.6 billion for border security .","depth":7},{"id":174,"text":"That bill would have funded fencing , beefed-up Border Patrol and Coast Guard staffing and new technology , but not a concrete wall .","depth":7},{"id":175,"text":"Ms. Capito said","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"she thought","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"that bill could serve as the group ' s starting point .","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"Mr. Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"whose own rhetoric about what he would consider to be a border wall","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"has often changed ,","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"has recently said","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"he isn ' t seeking a concrete barrier along the entirety of the border .","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"Earlier this month , the administration proposed adding 234 miles of steel slats and other physical barriers .","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"His latest proposal included $ 5.7 billion for steel barriers , as well as additional funds for drug-detection technology , more border agents , law-enforcement officials and immigration judges .","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"House Democrats had been preparing a proposal last week","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"outlining more than $ 5 billion in border-security enhancements","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"they supported ,","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"although they held back from releasing it","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"while Senate leaders pulled together the three-week spending bill","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"that reopened the government Friday night .","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"Those ideas are likely to be part of the coming negotiations .","depth":9},{"id":192,"text":"Should Mr. Trump declare a national emergency at the border ,","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"he could divert funds for military-construction projects","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"to fund a border wall ,","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"but such a move would certainly face legal challenges .","depth":10},{"id":196,"text":"Many congressional Republicans are also apprehensive","depth":11},{"id":197,"text":"it could set a precedent","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"that future Democratic presidents could declare a national emergency over their own priorities .","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"\" It ' ll be a terrible idea .","depth":13},{"id":200,"text":"I hope","depth":14},{"id":201,"text":"he doesn ' t do it , \"","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"( R. , Fla. )","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"said Sunday on NBC of the president ' s declaring a national emergency .","depth":13},{"id":205,"text":"Given the likelihood of a court challenge ,","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"\" you could very well wind up in sort of a theatric victory at the front end","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"and then not getting it done . \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":415,"left":306,"right":414,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":282,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":263,"right":281,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":236,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":225,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":220,"right":224,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":215,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":0,"right":214,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":214,"left":210,"right":213,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":210,"left":1,"right":209,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":209,"left"